Aim of this project is to implement of a low budget energy management system for low income houses in developing countries.

Another fact is that to implement this project to serve for commuintty where people do not bother about energy wastages.
by experienced , i have seen many people wasting the energy unnecessaraliy even themself know how energy is 
impotance to the cominity.

In this project , going to have a system which control everything by understanding user behaviour 



